## Serial Flashing
Complete guide on [Tasmota Docs](https://tasmota.github.io/docs/devices/Sonoff-S31)

### Buying Advice
When ordering check if it is indeed Sonoff S31 and not Sonoff S31 Lite which does not support power monitoring.
